2. Strict Prohibition of Use, Reference, and Copying

2.1 Prohibited Uses and Actions
The Licensee is explicitly prohibited from any of the following, unless the Licensor provides explicit, prior, and written consent:

    Content Creation and Streaming: The Licensee shall not use the Licensed Works, or any part thereof, in any publicly accessible media or platform, including but not limited to streaming services (e.g., Twitch, YouTube), social media posts, or any other form of media dissemination. This includes any form of content creation intended for public viewing, whether or not such activity results in any form of profit or material compensation.
